  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DUMMS! </strong> is a small Idler/Incremental game where you shoot at target dummies to gain XP, level up your skills, unlock quests and buy upgrades.<br>All of this with the goal of reaching the highest skills level possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destroy the dummies to gain XP.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras/472f9f566635b3a33064a7fc8f7cae4c.avif?t=1741097161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras_big/472f9f566635b3a33064a7fc8f7cae4c.avif?t=1741097161 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock \"SKILLS\" and level them up, buy \"QUESTS\" to gain rewards.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras/3be4cea7c110e2b4b979a890dedd7513.avif?t=1741097161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras_big/3be4cea7c110e2b4b979a890dedd7513.avif?t=1741097161 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Buy \"UPGRADES\" to make the game more interesting!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras/caba67a0d4b862dd9ef2a44599dee88a.avif?t=1741097161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras_big/caba67a0d4b862dd9ef2a44599dee88a.avif?t=1741097161 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short and active gameplay loop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Definite ending.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DUMMS! </strong> is a small Idler/Incremental game where you shoot at target dummies to gain XP, level up your skills, unlock quests and buy upgrades.<br>All of this with the goal of reaching the highest skills level possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destroy the dummies to gain XP.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras/472f9f566635b3a33064a7fc8f7cae4c.avif?t=1741097161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras_big/472f9f566635b3a33064a7fc8f7cae4c.avif?t=1741097161 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock \"SKILLS\" and level them up, buy \"QUESTS\" to gain rewards.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras/3be4cea7c110e2b4b979a890dedd7513.avif?t=1741097161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras_big/3be4cea7c110e2b4b979a890dedd7513.avif?t=1741097161 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Buy \"UPGRADES\" to make the game more interesting!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras/caba67a0d4b862dd9ef2a44599dee88a.avif?t=1741097161\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522420/extras_big/caba67a0d4b862dd9ef2a44599dee88a.avif?t=1741097161 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short and active gameplay loop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Definite ending.</p></li></ul>",
